In [19]:
distortions = []
K = range(1,10)

for k in K:
    kmeansmodel = KMeans(n_clusters = k)
    kmeansmodel.fit(x)
    distortions.append(kmeansmodel.inertia_)
In [20]:
plt.figure(figsize = (16,8))
plt.plot(K, distortions, 'bx-')
plt.xlabel('k')
plt.ylabel('Distortion')
plt.title('The Elbow Method Showing the Optimal CLusters')
plt.show()
